This package holds objects which represent abstract data which can be serialized.

    This method provides a way to call a method once for each of the elements of a list.

Package org.ensor.data.atom Description

This package holds objects which represent abstract data which can be serialized. The data in this package can be represented in a number of different ways including with XML, JSON, URL-encoded strings and other formats. The data carries no particular semantics other than the ability to represent and serialize it.
